@startuml folio-sequence-accept-review-invitation
' Folio — Reviewer accepts invitation (UC-03)
' Render: https://www.plantuml.com/plantuml

title Accept review invitation (UC-03)

actor Reviewer
participant "Folio UI" as UI
participant "Backend API\n(NestJS)" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ
participant "Email service" as Email

Reviewer -> UI : Open assignment;\ntap **Accept**
UI -> API : POST .../assignments/:slug/accept\n(JWT)

alt Not invited / not found
  API --> UI : 400 / 404
  UI --> Reviewer : Show error
else Success
  API -> DB : BEGIN transaction
  API -> DB : UPDATE assignment\nstatus = **accepted**

  opt Submission status was **submitted**
    API -> DB : UPDATE submission\nstatus = **under_review**
  end

  API -> DB : In-app notifications +\noutbox (invitation accepted)
  API -> DB : COMMIT

  API -> MQ : Publish events
  API --> UI : Accepted
  UI --> Reviewer : Can read manuscript

  MQ -> Email : Notify editors /\njournal managers
end

@enduml
